      <title>由于对美国支持的谨慎态度，乌克兰债券小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ukraine-bonds-edge-higher-as-caution-prevails-after-us-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰硬通货债券周一小幅走高，因投资者消化了美国众议院周末批准的 610 亿美元援助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ukraine-bonds-edge-higher-as-caution-prevails-after-us-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罢工后中东紧张局势缓和，金价回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东地缘政治紧张局势缓和、避险需求减少，以及交易员期待美国数据将揭示货币政策前景，金价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行维勒鲁瓦称石油不确定性不会阻止六月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-oil-uncertainty-won-t-stop-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加豪 (Francois Villeroy de Galhau) 表示，欧洲央行不会因油价不确定性而放弃 6 月份的首次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-oil-uncertainty-won-t-stop-june-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
